<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[الشَّوِيّ]</span>: جمع: شاءٍ،<span class="c5"> مثل كَليب:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>جمع كلب.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
